                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "Built a comprehensive POS and inventory management system for a retail and wholesale distribution business, supporting multi-channel sales (warehouse, van sales and customer stock), role-based access control (Admin, Sales Admin, Van Sales).\n\nThe platform unifies sales invoicing (cash & credit), purchase order management, inter-location inventory transfers, and advanced financial summary reporting with margin calculations, creating a seamless operation flow from warehouse to customer.",
